    "biasedText": "The document is the latest - and clearest - expression of Trump's desire to shake up the post-World War Two order led by the United States and built on a network of alliances and multilateral groups, and redefine it through his \"America First\" lens.",
    "explanation": "Phrases like \"shake up the post-World War Two order\" and \"redefine it through his 'America First' lens\" use dramatic language to emphasize upheaval and change, heightening the sense of disruption beyond a straightforward description."
